      <S N="ReleaseNotes">## [9.1.0] - 2025-05-09_x000D__x000A__x000D__x000A_### Changed_x000D__x000A__x000D__x000A_- Added the following resources:_x000D__x000A_  - **DnsClientNrptGlobal**: Configure DNS Client global Name Resolution Policy Table (NRPT) settings._x000D__x000A_  - **DnsClientNrptRule**: Sets a DNS Client NRPT rule on a node._x000D__x000A__x000D__x000A_- Updated CHANGELOG.md_x000D__x000A_  - Renamed NetworkingDSc to NetworkingDsc in CHANGELOG.md - fixes [Issue #513](https://github.com/dsccommunity/NetworkingDsc/issues/513)._x000D__x000A_- CI Pipeline_x000D__x000A_  - Updated pipeline files to match current DSC Community patterns - fixes [Issue #528](https://github.com/dsccommunity/NetworkingDsc/issues/528)._x000D__x000A_  - Updated HQRM and build steps to use windows-latest image._x000D__x000A_  - Update build pipeline to pin GitVersion v5._x000D__x000A_  - Added Server 2025 into Unit and Integration tests._x000D__x000A_  - Remove duplicated pipeline steps and use matrix of VM images._x000D__x000A_  - Use ModuleFast_x000D__x000A_  - Merge Unit test CodeCoverage_x000D__x000A_- Tests_x000D__x000A_  - Update to use Pester 5._x000D__x000A_- `New-InvalidArgumentException` change to `New-ArgumentException` for HQRM._x000D__x000A_- `NetworkingDsc.Common`_x000D__x000A_  - Changed to a buildable module._x000D__x000A__x000D__x000A_### Fixed_x000D__x000A__x000D__x000A_- `DSC_Firewall`_x000D__x000A_  - Fixed comment typo._x000D__x000A_  - Fixed `ParameterList` in `Set-TargetResource` typo._x000D__x000A_  - Remove `DisplayGroup` property when creating new firewall rule._x000D__x000A_  - `Test-RuleProperties`_x000D__x000A_    - Fixed `Convert-CIDRToSubnetMask` function call typo._x000D__x000A__x000D__x000A_### Removed_x000D__x000A__x000D__x000A_- `Build.psd1`_x000D__x000A_  - Removed as not required._x000D__x000A_- `DSC_IPAddress`_x000D__x000A_  - Remove IPv6 prefix length as unused._x000D__x000A_- `CommonTestHelper`_x000D__x000A_  - Use `Get-InvalidArgumentRecord` from `DscResource.Test`.</S>
